name: One Last Flight on Air Canada's 767! Business Class Toronto to Orlando
description:
Back in December 2019, I flew Air Canada's 767 from Toronto to Orlando, in their Business Class! Little did I know at the time, it would actually be my very last flight on a mainline Air Canada 767,  as they were all retired just 6 months later.

Seeing as it's been around a year now since these aircraft left passenger service, I thought I'd share that final flight with you all today!

Route: Toronto-Pearson (YYZ) - Orlando (MCO)
